# Instant UI Updates for Category Management - Implementation Report

## Problem Solved
**Issue**: User reported that subcategories would disappear from the UI only after manually refreshing the page, making the deletion process feel slow and unresponsive.

**Solution**: Implemented instant UI updates using optimistic updates with proper error recovery.

## 🚀 Implementation Details

### **Instant UI Updates for Deletion**

#### **Subcategory Deletion (Lines 151-187)**
```javascript
// Before API call: Update local state immediately
setCategories(prevCategories => {
  const updatedCategories = prevCategories.map(category => {
    if (category.id === categoryId) {
      return {
        ...category,
        Subcategory: (category.Subcategory || []).filter(subcat => subcat.id !== subcategoryId)
      };
    }
    return category;
